page.title: 14My family's weekend
page.content: My name is Emma Carrington. I have 1 brother and a sister. I am going to tell you what our family did last weekend June 14th to 17th.On Friday we go shopping at Sainburys. On Saturday my sister and I and my brother go to Ripley Tennis Club and we entered a tennis tournament.My mum stayed at home and mowed the grass.On Sunday we went a walk.When we came back we put the pregnant guinea pigs in a box.Samatha Roper came over and we went to Sarah's Party.(Sarah is a friend).My mum and Julian stayed at home and had tea.
